Strings.achievement.100rooms: GET THE SNOW ON THE ROAD
Strings.achievement.gobstopper_desc: Destroy 10 different paintings of Goblin, the mysterious black cat.
Strings.achievement.nodamage_desc: Complete five consecutive rooms without taking damage.
Strings.achievement.quick_clear_desc: Clear a room in under four seconds.
Strings.calendar.day1_desc:
Five hundred free <color=orange>stars</color> to spend in the shop. More interesting rewards are coming, this is just because hardly anyone will play on the first day.

Reward for day 1.
Strings.calendar.day2_desc:
A snowman-themed <color=orange>shotgun</color> which smiles idly as it watches you consume the blood of your enemies. Textured by <color=orange>zelzmiy</color> and <color=orange>Fri</color>.

Reward for day 2.
Strings.calendar.day3_desc:
A candy cane patterned <color=orange>banner</color>. By the way, I forgot to implement a <color=orange>update notification</color>, so if you are on the first version (2.0.1) please update.

Reward for day 3.
Strings.calendar.day5_desc:
Exhibit is level designed by <color=orange>Fri</color>, where you search for presents in a fine art gallery. A <color=orange>banner</color> of the level is included.

Reward for day 5.
Strings.calendar.day6_desc:
Five hundred free <color=orange>stars</color> to spend in the shop. It's boring filler, but if I do all the skins at once I'll run out. Better things will be tomorrow.

Reward for day 6.
Strings.calendar.day7_desc:
A sweet railcannon skin designed by <color=orange>Takovic</color>, made entirely out of gingerbread and candy canes, and covered in multicoloured sprinkes.

Reward for day 7.
Strings.calendar.day8_desc:
A gingerbread slab revolver skin designed by <color=orange>Takovic</color>, coated in icing. New content update tomorrow, by the way, as long as I finish it.

Reward for day 8.
Strings.calendar.day9_desc:
A radiant candy cane banner to celebrate <color=orange>DD 2.1</color>, which adds special waves, such as radiance, fireworks, and idol wards, all after room 20.

Reward for day 9.
Strings.calendar.day10_desc:
A present skin themed after a <color=orange>TV</color>. I have no idea how they stay on without any power.


Reward for day 10.
Strings.calendar.day11_desc:
Previous advent calendar rewards have become <color=orange>purchasable</color> for 1000 stars. Here's 500 stars to get you started on buying anything you missed.

Reward for day 11.
Strings.calendar.day12_desc:
The first <color=orange>sawblade launcher skin</color> in the mod, created by Fri. It is themed after an ugly Christmas sweater.


Reward for day 12.
Strings.calendar.day13_desc:
An evil and malicious collection of <color=orange>killer robots</color>. This banner contains V1, V2, V3, and V4, all together.


Reward for day 13.
